   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Forest preservation in Mexico Manos a la Tierra</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Each year 4.7 million acres of forest are lost in the world, exacerbating the effects of climate change. For 14 years, Manos a la Tierra has inspired thousands of volunteers to join activities for the preservation of forests, planting around 450,000 trees in Mexico without any financial support. Your donation would allow us to carry out more reforestations, river cleanings, pest control, prevention and control of forest fires and soil regeneration and the purchase of the necessary equipment.</narrative>
  </description>
